=== Cultural properties ===
=== Important Intangible Folk Cultural Property (nationally designated) ===
* Mitsuke Tenjin Hadaka Matsuri - Designated {{ill|lt=December 27|Q2800|WD=Q2800|1=December 27}}, {{ill|lt=2000|Q1985|WD=Q1985|1=2000}}
** A festival centered on the ritual procession (togyo) in which the deity of Yanahime Shrine proceeds to {{ill|lt=Ōmi Kunitama Shrine|Q43594535|WD=Q43594535|1=Ōmi Kunitama Shrine}}, the {{ill|lt=sōja|Q1107129|WD=Q1107129|1=Sōja shrine}} of {{ill|lt=Tōtōmi Province|Q11642126|WD=Q11642126|1=Tōtōmi}}. It is held on the Saturday and Sunday immediately before the 10th day of the 8th month of the old calendar<ref name="見付天神裸祭"/>.

